{"tid":2344652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界入黎 有冇人覺得下波疫情會係家庭群組爆發","createTime":"2020-12-29T02:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T04:50:36.000Z","uid":126889,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4387752bf28c1715c3724d2414190a9459f377c0","tid":2344652,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"香港人居住空間咁窄<br />\n普通家庭都講緊3-5個<br />\n已經好易超哂政府限眾令要求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據專家講法 成日都係咁樣眾集好易傳播<br />\n一家人又唔知邊個去過邊<br />\n大家圍埋一齊又易做親密既野（局長語）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飯同沖涼係家庭最危險既事<br />\n食飯唔洗講 飯餸未齊 有人就可以除低罩食舊先 好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圍埋一齊食飯夾餸 好容易交換病毒<br />\n係屋企咁放鬆既環境 好易忘記要嚴謹抗疫<br />\n<br />\n沖涼唔洗講 除哂衫除埋口罩等保護<br />\n 你係要冒上極大感染風險 病毒可以直接接觸人體 而沙士經驗話我地聽水渠果啲咁近好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情好嚴峻<br />\n食飯應該係房食<br />\n沖涼唔係要洗頭應該都建議戴口罩<br />\n人人出房都戴口罩先 如果唔係都幾自私<br />\n<br />\n本來諗住講大家扑野最好都上罩 <br />\n插入前用消毒酒精洗下碌鳩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但考慮到抗疫同生活應該有個平衡點 大家都係盡量避免打車輪 唔係好容易有埋扑野群組<br />\n唔好自私撚 thanks🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"1eacc7fc92bb41a4266d81ff78ddbf79d146c94a","tid":2344652,"uid":9193,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"錯 全部都係林鄭月娥唔封關群組"},{"pid":"7134d23689b68e3cc954ca7ba726cb59c1a42ba1","tid":2344652,"uid":105924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"假膠? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1becfaf51f34e027ac17cefdccb54672f455e61","tid":2344652,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1eacc7fc92bb41a4266d81ff78ddbf79d146c94a","tid":2344652,"uid":9193,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"錯 全部都係林鄭月娥唔封關群組"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:35:49.000Z","msg":"關口已經有好嚴格抗疫措施保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但家庭群組冇<br />\n應該立例監管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfbf23d2662d467458c4d9a60b1500f2f29977c","tid":2344652,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7134d23689b68e3cc954ca7ba726cb59c1a42ba1","tid":2344652,"uid":105924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"假膠? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家疫情嚴峻"},{"pid":"65fcef33d6f3b03267ab629a38f6e7da6fc4780d","tid":2344652,"uid":105924,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"dbfbf23d2662d467458c4d9a60b1500f2f29977c","tid":2344652,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7134d23689b68e3cc954ca7ba726cb59c1a42ba1","tid":2344652,"uid":105924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"假膠? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家疫情嚴峻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:41:43.000Z","msg":"為左防疫，我覺得政府最好&hellip;<br />\n1. 用緊急法宵禁同強制要屋企所有成員隔開1.5米距離<br />\n2. 將口罩令延伸至私人地方，特別係屋企<br />\n3. 立法擴大警察權力任意強行搜查私人地方是否遵守政府防疫法例<br />\n4. 立法禁止售賣condom以免有扑野群組<br />\n做哂以上呢四點香港班防疫塔利班應該好開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91991e5ce0e8baac0a22c11b2ca080e9c8ea6cc8","tid":2344652,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score